msgid "A classic 9 × 9 sudoku game"
msgstr "Een klassiek 9 x 9 sudoku spel"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.pumoku.metainfo.xml:28
msgid ""
"PuMoKu is a classic, 9 × 9 Sudoku solving game aimed for Plasma Mobile. It "
"comes with flexible highlighting options and (touch) input methods, full "
"undo stack and more."
msgstr ""
"PuMoKu is een klassiek, 9 x 9 pumoku oplosspel gericht op Plasma Mobiel. Het "
"komt met flexibele accentueringsopties en (aanraak) invoermethoden, stapel "
"voor volledig ongedaan maken en meer."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.pumoku.metainfo.xml:30
msgid "Input methods: Cell first, Number first or Hybrid"
msgstr "Invoermethoden: cel eerst, getal eerst of hybride"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.pumoku.metainfo.xml:31
msgid "Built in sudoku generator"
msgstr "Ingebouwde sudoku generator"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
